history.content: Hello! How can I help you today?

I am Gemini, a multi-modal AI model, developed by Google. I am designed to provide information and assist people with a wide range of tasks and questions.

Unlike traditional search engines that simply provide a list of links, I can understand and respond to complex questions in a conversational way. I can also generate text, translate languages, write different kinds of creative content, and perform many other tasks.

I am still under development, but I am learning new things every day. I am excited to see how I can continue to help people in the future.

Is there anything I can help you with today?
